[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man seriously hurt after Swansea knife attack

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been arrested after another man was attacked with a knife in Swansea.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
South Wales Police said the 24-year-old was in a serious condition at Morriston Hospital following a disturbance at 00:15 GMT in St Helen's Avenue in the city centre.
A 22-year-old local man is in custody.
